We will be developing a 2d sandbox game in which the player can freely choose what to do.
The player will be spawned in a procedurally generated world and will be able to dig and fight.
By digging the player gathers resources.
With those resources he can build new items and become more powerful.

M1

- Pick technology.
- Research procedural generation.
- Basic player models.
- Movement.
- Basic world (procedural if possible).
- Digging.

M2

- Items
- Digging yields items.
- Crafting.
- Enemies.

M3

- Enemy AI.
- Improved procedural generation.
- Harder survival.
- Player stats.
- Special places.
